    <abstract>
      <t>&lt;p&gt;This document specifies new Internet Key Exchange Protocol Version 2 (IKEv2) notification status types to better manage IPv4 and IPv6 coexistence by allowing the responder to signal to the initiator which address families are allowed.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;This document updates RFC 7296.&lt;/p&gt;</t>
